{"tid":2084562,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"黃秋生原定台灣拍宣傳片開價60萬 當地「觀傳局」嚇得合作破局","createTime":"2020-06-29T10:05:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T13:12:16.000Z","uid":235152,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3fa6643917e4420da5f3bbedc0ce62ee2e179185","tid":2084562,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:05:30.000Z","msg":"影帝黃秋生遭內地封殺後，演出機會大減，而近日他決定到台灣拍戲，<br />\n還計畫移民至當地。根據當地傳媒報導，黃秋生來台拍戲其實片酬不高，<br />\n但認為只要有戲拍，酬勞低一點開始也沒關係，剛好最近台北市政府觀傳局，<br />\n想邀他為西門町的影音街拍攝宣傳影片，製作單位向黃秋生經紀人詢價，<br />\n酬勞要60萬港幣，讓製作單位嚇到，想要進一步詢問是否有議價空間，<br />\n遭已讀不回，最後雙方合作破局。"},{"pid":"b5edb05d1fcc3e2d291edcb155566fcef1434270","tid":2084562,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:07:13.000Z","msg":"source"},{"pid":"032aad90ee3fc2250f640d85b4aca777f7e9dcca","tid":2084562,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"b5edb05d1fcc3e2d291edcb155566fcef1434270","tid":2084562,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:07:13.000Z","msg":"source"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:09:28.000Z","msg":"流動新聞唔想貼<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.msn.com/zh-hk/entertainment/news/%E9%BB%83%E7%A7%8B%E7%94%9F%E5%8E%9F%E5%AE%9A%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%8B%8D%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3%E7%89%87%E9%96%8B%E5%83%B960%E8%90%AC-%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%B0-%E8%A7%80%E5%82%B3%E5%B1%80-%E5%9A%87%E5%BE%97%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E7%A0%B4%E5%B1%80/ar-BB165pUW?ocid=msedgntp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msn.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fentertainment%2Fnews%2F%25E9%25BB%2583%25E7%25A7%258B%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%258B%258D%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%2582%25B3%25E7%2589%2587%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%2583%25B960%25E8%2590%25AC-%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%259C%25B0-%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%25B1%2580-%25E5%259A%2587%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25BD%259C%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E5%25B1%2580%2Far-BB165pUW%3Focid%3Dmsedgntp&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTSrXKCTJ71YGEIw